<br>
How do people interpret that.  Certainly it doesn't mean RP is mandatory at all times.  But it does seem a lot stronger than to say RP is optional. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=dalninil>Dalninil</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 460<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(9/25/02 3:59:34 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1454.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Verant's take on RPing on this server</span><hr size=1> and ? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/usyllestraefv.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Syllestrae FV</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Moderating inconsistently<br>since Jun 2002</span><br>  Posts: 1314<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(9/25/02 4:01:19 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1454.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Verant's take on RPing on this server</span><hr size=1> In theory, I suppose it's like saying &quot;You don't have to RP, but the community may give you flak if you don't&quot;.<br>
<br>
In practice, I think they might as well have just labelled this the crazy tradable loot server.  The existing rules-set is much more appealing to loot hunters / ubers than it is to roleplayers.  The roleplayers are here just cuz it's kind of a designated gathering area, and so you're more likely to find roleplay done (or at least tolerated) here.<br>
<br>
RPing on some of the blue servers you get made fun of, etc.<br>
<br>
- Syll <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/uenedlithien.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Enedlithien</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.shadow-striders.com/images/wolfIcon.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Elle est trés jolie</span><br>  Posts: 182<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(9/25/02 4:59:56 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1454.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.cpinternet.com/~theduke/MythStuff/ez-tres.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Verant's take on RPing on this server</span><hr size=1> If they would have said &quot;roleplay required&quot; they would have been responsible for creating rules and enforcing them.  <br>
